      "target": "pdpa-2010",
      "type": "references",
      "reason": "A cloud region outside Malaysia engages the PDPA's cross-border transfer test (substantially similar law or adequate protection), so the 17.1 notification should still capture data residency once the requirement to consult the Bank is removed.",
